Bank of America Sued by American Asset Over Asset-Backed Loans

-- B y   J e r a n   W i t t e n s t e i n
-- 
2011-10-18T18:25:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/bank-of-america-sued-by-american-asset-over-asset-backed-loans.html
Bank of America Corp. (BAC)  was sued by
American Asset Corp., a real-estate company, over asset-backed
loans in Charlotte and Raleigh,  North Carolina .  The loans are managed by American Asset Corp., the company
said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jeran Wittenstein at 
 jwittenstei1@bloomberg.net  